Subject: Re: [T2] lock interchangeability

> It's the sliding door and front door handles, rear hatch and ignition.
 
The rear hatch latch is opposite between L code and R code. 
On L code, the catch pin is on the left end to the left of the 2 screws.
On the R code, your 71, the catch pin is in the middle between the 2 screws.

You may be able to swap the catches that mount to the body but I doubt it. 
